\id HEB Bible in Fouta-Jalon Pular 
\mt1 ЖЃATAKURU NAЖЃANAANDU YAHUUDIYANKEEЖЃE ЖЃEN 
\c 1  
\s1 Fii no Iisaa Almasiihu on ЖЃurdi Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en 
\p  
\v 1 Nde wonnoo Alla yewtiriino maamiraaЙ“e men Й“en annabaaЙ“e Й“en laawi buy e nooneeji buy,  
\v 2 Alla yewtirii en ka ЙІalaaЙ—e sakkitore Й—oo ЖЃiЙ—Й—o on. O waЙ—i mo ronoowo e kala huunde, awa ko on o tagiri aduna on.  
\v 3 Ko on ЖЃiЙ—Й—o woni jalbeendi annoora Alla on, ko kanko woni mbaadi Alla ndin tigi. Ko on ЖЃiЙ—Й—o woni tambitiiЙ—o kala huunde rewrude e daaluyee makko dolnuЙ—o on. Nde o laatinnoo laЙ“Й“ingol yimЙ“e Й“en junuubaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, o jooЙ—oyii ka sengo ЙІaamo Alla MawЙ—o on ka kammuuli,  
\v 4 o woni Й“urЙ—o malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en, wano innde nde o roni nden Й“urdiri Й—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en non. 
\p  
\v 5 Ko fii ko hombo e malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en Alla daalani: 
\q1 В«Ko an woni ЖЃiЙ—Й—o an on, hande a wonii mo anВ»,\f a \fr 1:5 \ft 1.5a Zab. 2.7 \f* 
\m maa o daalani kadi: 
\q1 В«Mi wonanay mo Baaba, 
\q1 o wonanammi ЖЃiЙ—Й—o.В»?\f b \fr 1:5 \ft 1.5b 2Sam 7.14 \f* 
\m  
\v 6 ЖЃay o addii Afo on ka nder aduna, o daali kadi: 
\q1 В«Yo malaa'ikaaЙ“e Alla Й“en fow sujjan mo.В» 
\m  
\v 7 Fii malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en o daali: 
\q1 В«O waЙ—ay malaa'ikaaЙ“e makko Й“en hendu 
\q1 e kurkaaЙ—i makko Й—in Й—enЙ—e yiite.В»\f c \fr 1:7 \ft 1.7 Zab. 104.4 \f* 
\m  
\v 8 Kono fii ЖЃiЙ—Й—o on o daali: 
\q1 В«Jullere maa laamu nden, yaa an Alla, luttay haa poomaa, 
\q1 labbooru maa laamu ndun ko labbooru peewal. 
\q1  
\v 9 A yiЙ—ii peewal ngal, a aЙІii angal peewal ngal. 
\q1 Ko Й—un waЙ—i si Alla JoomiraaЙ—o maa on 
\q1 toЙ—Й—or maa nebban weltaare Й“uri wondiЙ“Й“e maa Й“en.В» \f d \fr 1:9 \ft 1.9 Zab. 45.7-8 \f* 
\m  
\v 10 E hoore Й—un o daali kadi: 
\q1 В«Yaa an JoomiraaЙ—o, ko an wallini ndelo leydi ndin ka fuЙ—Й—oode, 
\q1 awa kadi kammuuli Й—in ko juuЙ—e maa Й—en tagiraa. 
\p  
\v 11 ЖЉi lannay, kono an a luttay, 
\q1 Й—i fow Й—i nawyiray wa dolokke, 
\q1  
\v 12 ЙІobbiraa Й—i wa waanaare, 
\q1 e hoore Й—un Й—i waylirte wa dolokke. 
\q1 Kono an a wa'ay no wa'uЙ—aa, 
\q1 awa kadi, duuЙ“i maa Й—in lannataa.В»\f Й— \fr 1:12 \ft 1.12 Zab. 102.26-28 \f* 
\m  
\v 13 E ko hombo e malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en o daalani: 
\q1 В«JooЙ—or ka sengo an ЙІaamo, 
\q1 haa mi waЙ—a ayЙ“e maa Й“en ka ley teppe maa.В»?\f e \fr 1:13 \ft 1.13 Zab. 110.1 \f* 
\m  
\v 14 Hara Й“ee malaa'ikaaЙ“e fow, hinaa Й“e ruuhuuji kurkotooЙ—i, nulaaЙ—i fii gollangol ronooЙ“e kisiyee Й“en? 
\c 2  
\s1 Fii Kisiyee MawЙ—o on 
\p  
\v 1 Ko Й—un waЙ—i, hiЙ—en haani cataade fota e ko nanuЙ—en kon, fii wota en selu.  
\v 2 Ko fii, si konguЙ—i Й—i malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en hewtini maamiraaЙ“e men Й“en Й—in haqinqinaama, awa kadi kala bonnere e noone geddi yoЙ“iraama ko handi kon,  
\v 3 haray ko honno daЙ—iroyten si en wedditike e sifa oo kisiyee mawЙ—o? Ko Joomi men on tigi adii feЙІЙІinde mo, onsay non nanunooЙ“e mo Й“en haqinqinani en.  
\v 4 Allaahu on seeditodi e maЙ“Й“e, o Й“anginiri Й—un kuuЙ—e e maandeeji e noone kaawakeeji moЖґЖґi e sendirgol dokke *Ruuhu SeniiЙ—o on wano o yiЙ—iri non. 
\s1 Fii ArdotooЙ—o YimЙ“e Й“en ka Kisiyee 
\p  
\v 5 Hinaa malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en Alla yankinani oo aduna aroyoowo mo wowleten fii mun on.  
\v 6 Kono goЙ—Й—o no seeditii nokku goo, wi'i: 
\q1 В«Ko honЙ—un woni neЙ—Й—o fii no anditiraa fii makko, yaa an Alla, 
\q1 e ko woni Й“ii neЙ—Й—anke fii yo a danko mo? 
\p  
\v 7 A waЙ—ii mo e ley malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en e nder seeЙ—a nii, 
\q1 a taaranii mo *meetelol mangu e teddungal, 
\q1 a waЙ—ii mo e hoore kuuЙ—e juuЙ—e maa Й—en, 
\q1  
\v 8 a waЙ—ii piiji Й—in fow e ley koyЙ—e makko.В»\f f \fr 2:8 \ft 2.6-8 Zab. 8.5-7 \f* 
\m E nder yankinangol mo piiji Й—in fow, alaa ko Alla acci yo ronku yankinanaade mo, kono haa jooni en yi'aali ka piiji Й—in fow yankinanii mo.  
\v 9 Kono non e hino ko tawЙ—en kon: Й“awto o waЙ—eede e ley malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en fii saa'ihun nii, kanko Iisaa o waЙ—anaama meetelol mangu e teddungal sabu mayde nde o tampiri nden, fii, tippude e moЖґЖґere Alla nden, yo o maayan yimЙ“e Й“en fow. 
\p  
\v 10 E dow ardagol fayЙ“e buy ka mangu, tawi no hawrani on TaguЙ—o piiji fow, e mo piiji Й—in fow wonani on, laatinirgol Iisaa timmuЙ—o e nder tampereeji, on SincuЙ—o kisiyee maЙ“Й“e on.  
\v 11 Ko fii, ko *laЙ“Й“inЙ—o on e *laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en fow woni iwdi wootiri. Ko Й—un waЙ—i kanko Iisaa o hersiraa noddirgol Й“e musiЙ“Й“e,  
\v 12 wano o wi'iri Alla non wonde: 
\q1 В«Mi jantanto musiЙ“Й“e an Й“en innde maa nden, 
\q1 mi mantoyte ka hakkunde tumbondiral.В»\f g \fr 2:12 \ft 2.12 Zab. 22.23 \f* 
\m  
\v 13 O wi'i kadi: 
\q1 В«Mi waЙ—ay hoolaare an nden e makko.В» 
\m Awa kadi: 
\q1 В«E hino lan, min e fayЙ“e Й“e Alla okkimmi Й“en.В»\f h \fr 2:13 \ft 2.13 Isa. 8.17-18 \f* 
\m  
\v 14 Awa nde tawnoo fayЙ“e Й“en no mari ЖґiiЖґan e Й“andu, kanko Iisaa kadi ko wano non o tawdiraa e maЙ“Й“e, fii, rewrude e mayde makko nden, yo o muncu on joginooЙ—o bawgal mayde nden, Й—un ko Ibuliisa,  
\v 15 e fii yo o jattin kala wonnooЙ“e e nder maccangaaku e nder ngurndan mun sabu kulol mayde.  
\v 16 ЖЃay, pellet wonaa malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en o ari faabagol, kono ko jurriya Ibraahiima on o ari faabagol.  
\v 17 Ko Й—un waЙ—i si himo haanunoo nandude e musiЙ“Й“e makko Й“en few, fii no o wonira *yottinoowo mawЙ—o sadaka ka Alla, yurmeteeЙ—o, holniiЙ—o e nder golle Alla Й—en, fii no jamaa on heЙ“ira yaafuyee junuubaaji.  
\v 18 ЖЃay kanko tigi o tampii fewndo o ndarndaa, himo waawi faabaade wonaaЙ“e e ndarndeede Й“en. 
\c 3  
\s1 Fii no Iisaa Almasiihu on ЖЃurdiri Muusaa 
\p  
\v 1 Ko Й—un waЙ—i, yo musiЙ“Й“e an laaЙ“uЙ“e, Й“e mi hawti noddaandu Alla ndun, feЕ‹ee miijo mon ngon e hoore mo Alla toЙ—Й—ii neli on, on *Yottinoowo mawЙ—o sadaka ka Alla, on mo qirritiЙ—en ka gomЙ—inal men, Й—un ko Iisaa.  
\v 2 O wonno sella-findeejo e telen-ma on ToЙ—Й—iiЙ—o mo, wano Muusaa wonirnoo non e nder suudu Alla ndun fow.  
\v 3 E hoore Й—un, tawaama ko o RinЙ—anЙ—o mangu Й“uri ngu Muusaa ngun, ko fii darnuЙ—o suudu on no mari teddungal Й“uri suudu ndun tigi.  
\v 4 Ko fii kala suudu ko goЙ—Й—o darni Й—un, kono ko kanko Alla darni kala huunde.  
\v 5 Muusaa kaЙІun wonno kurkaadu sella-findeejo e nder suudu Alla ndun fow, fii seeditagol ko Alla daaloyta kon.  
\v 6 Kono *Almasiihu on kan ko ЖЃiЙ—Й—o sella-findeejo e hoore suudu Alla ndun. Ko enen woni suudu makko ndun, si en catike fota e wakkilaare e hoolaare nde jogiЙ—en fii ko tanЖґiniЙ—en kon. 
\s1 Fii Fowtaare Maranaande Jamaa Alla on nden 
\p  
\v 7 Ko Й—un waЙ—i, wano *Ruuhu SeniiЙ—o on wi'iri non: 
\q1 В«Si on nanii kongol makko ngol hande, 
\q1  
\v 8 wota on sattin Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en, 
\q1 wa fewndo maamiraaЙ“e mon Й“en murtannoo mi, 
\q1 Й“e ndarndii mi ka wulaa, 
\q1  
\v 9 ka Й“e liggitunoo mi Й—on, Й“e ndarndii mi, 
\q1 Й“e yi'uno kuuЙ—e an Й—en e nder duuЙ“i cappanЙ—e nay. 
\p  
\v 10 Ko Й—un waЙ—i si mi tikkani ngun jamaanu, mi wi'i: 
\q1 вЂ№ЖЃerЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko seluЙ—e saa'i kala, 
\q1 Й“e andaali laawi an Й—in.вЂє 
\p  
\v 11 Mi woonduno e nder tikkere an nden wonde: 
\q1 вЂ№ЖЃe naatataa ka fowtaare an few!вЂє В»\f i \fr 3:11 \ft 3.7-11 Zab. 95.7-11 \f* 
\m  
\v 12 Awa, reenee, yo musiЙ“Й“e, fii wota hay gooto e mon heЙ“u Й“ernde bonnde e Й“ernde nde gomЙ—inal tabitaa e mun, haa ka yiltoЙ—on e Й“aawo Alla WuuruЙ—o on.  
\v 13 Kono wakkilindiree hakkunde mon ЙІande woo, yeru no wi'eede hande, fii wota hay gooto e mon sattinir Й“ernde mun Й—aynireede junuubu.  
\v 14 Ko fii en wonii kafiduЙ“e e Almasiihu on, si tawii en jogitike fota pellital men aranal ngal haa ka sakkitorun,  
\v 15 wano bindi Й—in wi'iri non wonde: 
\q1 В«Hande si on nanii hito makko ngon, 
\q1 wota on sattin Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en 
\q1 wa fewndo murtaldu ndun.В»\f j \fr 3:15 \ft 3.15 Zab. 95.7-8 \f* 
\m  
\v 16 Ko homЙ“e woni Й“en murtannooЙ“e Alla, Й“awto Й“e nanude kongol makko ngol? Hinaa Й“ee Й“e Muusaa ardinoo, yaltini *Misira?  
\v 17 E ko homЙ“e woni Й“en Й“e Alla tikkannoo e nder Й—ii duuЙ“i cappanЙ—e nay? Hinaa Й“ee waЙ—unooЙ“e junuubu, maayi ka wulaa?  
\v 18 E ko homЙ“e o woondannoo naatataa ka fowtaare makko, si hinaa yedduЙ“e Й“en?  
\v 19 Awa en yi'ii Й“e waawaali naatude ka fowtaare makko, sabu angal gomЙ—inal. 
\c 4  
\p  
\v 1 Ko Й—un waЙ—i, yeru fodaari fii naatugol ka fowtaare makko no lutti, haray hulen wota goЙ—Й—o e mon aru e tawdeede e ronkooЙ“e naatude Й“en.  
\v 2 Ko fii Kibaaru MoЖґЖґo on feЙІЙІinanaama en, wano Й“eya non, kono kongol ngol Й“e heЙ—ii ngol nafaali Й“e huunde, ko fii ko Й“e nanunoo kon, Й“e jaЙ“iraano gomЙ—inal.  
\v 3 Kono enen gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, en naatay e nden fowtaare nde o innunoo wonde: 
\q1 В«Mi woondii e nder tikkere an nden, 
\q1 Й“e naatataa ka fowtaare an few!В»\f k \fr 4:3 \ft 4.3 Zab. 95.11 \f* 
\m E hin-le, Alla gayniino golle mun Й—en gila ka fuЙ—Й—oode aduna on.  
\v 4 Ko fii himo daali nokku goo ka bindi fii ЙІalaande jeeЙ—iЙ—aЙ“ere nden wonde: 
\q1 В«Ka ЙІalaande jeeЙ—iЙ—aЙ“ere Alla fowtino e golleeji makko Й—in fow.В»\f m \fr 4:4 \ft 4.4 FuЙ—. 2.2 \f* 
\m  
\v 5 Himo daali kadi fahin Й—oo: 
\q1 В«ЖЃe naatataa ka fowtaare an few!В»\f n \fr 4:5 \ft 4.5 Zab. 95.11 \f* 
\m  
\v 6 Nde tawnoo no heddanii woЙ“Й“e goo fii naatoygol ton, e hin-le kadi attinooЙ“e hendaade Kibaaru MoЖґЖґo on kaЙІun naataano sabu angal gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal,  
\v 7 e yeeso Й—un buy Allaahu on daaluno kadi iwrude e Daawuuda, o toЙ—Й—ii ЙІalaande, o inni nden В«handeВ», wano siforanoo non dow Й—oo: 
\q1 В«Hande si on nanii hito makko ngon, 
\q1 wota on sattin Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en.В»\f ЙІ \fr 4:7 \ft 4.7 Zab. 95.7 \f* 
\m  
\v 8 Si tawiino Yaasuwa\f Е‹ \fr 4:8 \ft 4.8 Ko \+it В«YaasuwaВ»\+it* on wondunoo e Muusaa fewndo o Жґawata ka fello. Ko Yaasuwa on ardinoo jamaa Isra'iila on, naadi Й“e leydi fodaandi ndin.\f* yeЙ—iino Й“e nden fowtaare, Alla wowlataano Й“awto Й—un fii ЙІalaande goo.  
\v 9 Awa jaka no lutti *ЙІalaande fowteteende e mun fii jamaa Alla on.  
\v 10 Ko fii kala naatuЙ—o ka fowtaare Alla, o fowtoto kadi e golle makko Й—en, wano Alla fowtornoo Й—e mun Й—en non. 
\p  
\v 11 Awa etoЙ—en naatugol ka fowtaare makko Й—on, fii wota hay gooto falju, jokka Й“e Й—oftaaki Й“en. 
\p  
\v 12 Ko fii, daaluyee Alla on ko wuuruЙ—o duncoowo, himo weli Й“uri kaafa ka mbelЙ—e Й—iЙ—i, ko naatayЙ—o haa hakkunde ruuhu e wonkii, e hakkunde jokke e mbuso, o ЙІaawa mbeleeЙ—e e miijooji Й“ernde.  
\v 13 Alaa ko tagaa ko o yi'ataa, fow no wallinaa, waЙ—aa e kene yeeso on mo hunoytoЙ—en. 
\s1 Fii no Iisaa Woniri Yottinoowo MawЙ—o Sadaka 
\p  
\v 14 ЖЃay hiЙ—en mari hooreejo mawЙ—o *yottinooЙ“e sadaka ka Alla, taЖґituЙ—o kammuuli Й—in, Й—un ko Iisaa *ЖЃiЙ—Й—o Alla on, catoЙ—en e qirritannde gomЙ—inal men ngal.  
\v 15 Ko fii en maraa yottinoowo mawЙ—o mo waawataa faamude lo'ere men nden, kono o ndarndoranooma wano men non e Й—i fow, e hoore o waЙ—aali junuubu.  
\v 16 Awa Й“adoren hoolaare ka jullere laamu, ka sulfu on heЙ“oytoo ton, fii no heЙ“iren yurmeende e moЖґЖґere ko wonana en ballal fewndo haanani en. 
\c 5  
\p  
\v 1 Awa, kala *yottinoowo mawЙ—o sadaka ka Alla, suЙ“aaЙ—o e hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en, ko joЙ—Й—iniraa ko fii yimЙ“e Й“en, fii ko waЙ—a golleeji Alla Й—in, fii no Й“e weeЙ“itira dokke e sadakaaji fii junuubaaji Й—in.  
\v 2 Himo waawi yurmeede Й“e faamaa Й“en e seluЙ“e Й“en, ko fii kanko tigi lo'ereeji no hundi mo.  
\v 3 Awa ko sabu nden lo'ere waЙ—i si himo haani ittande hoore makko sadaka, o ittana jamaa on kadi sadakaaji fii junuubaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in.  
\v 4 Kono hay gooto waawataa heЙ“ande hoore mun ngal teddungal wonugol yottinoowo mawЙ—o sadaka. Ko Alla yeЙ—ata Й—un, wano o toЙ—Й—ori *Haaruuna non. 
\p  
\v 5 Ko wano non kadi, hinaa *Almasiihu on tigi yeЙ—i hoore mun ngal teddungal wonugol yottinoowo mawЙ—o sadaka ka Alla, kono ko Wi'uЙ—o mo on wonde: 
\q1 В«Ko an woni ЖЃiЙ—Й—o an on, hande a wonii mo an.В»\f p \fr 5:5 \ft 5.5 Zab. 2.7 \f* 
\m  
\v 6 Wano non himo wi'i kadi nokku goo: 
\q1 В«Ko a yottinoowo sadaka ka Alla haa poomaa wano *Maaliki-Siddiiqu non.В»\f q \fr 5:6 \ft 5.6 Zab. 110.4 \f* 
\m  
\v 7 E hoore Й—un, e nder ngurndan makko Й—an ka hoore leydi, kanko Iisaa o weeЙ“itanno on Gasoowo mo dandude mayde nden gonЙ—i e torndeeji e nder ewnagol ko tiiЙ—i. Alla jaabinani mo sabu ko o yankinaninoo mo kon.  
\v 8 Fii kala ko o *ЖЃiЙ—Й—o Alla, o andi ko woni Й—oftaare e nder ko o tampi kon fow.  
\v 9 ЖЃay wonii o waЙ—aama TimmuЙ—o, o wonani Й—oftiiЙ“e mo Й“en fow Й“undu kisiyee poomayankeejo.  
\v 10 Onsay Alla toЙ—Й—ii mo yottinoowo mawЙ—o sadaka ka Alla wano Maaliki-Siddiiqu non. 
\s1 Fii Reenagol e Selugol GomЙ—inal 
\p  
\v 11 HiЙ—en mari piiji buy ko wowlen e fii Й—un, hara ko piiji buy mettuЙ—i sifaade, ko fii on wonii mettuЙ“e faaminde.  
\v 12 E hin-le, e oo saa'i Й—oo hiЙ—on haanunoo wonude jannooЙ“e, kono hiЙ—on handi kadi e janneede Жґi'al daaluyeeji Alla Й—in. Fewndo Й—oo ko Й“ira handuЙ—on e mun, hinaa ЙІaametee.  
\v 13 On jokkuЙ—o yarugol Й“ira, haray alaa faamu woo e fii daaluyee faaminayЙ—o ngurndan feewuЙ—an Й—an, ko fii haray haa jooni ootigi ko boobo.  
\v 14 MokobaaЙ“e Й“en kaЙІun, ko ЙІaametee tedduЙ—o Й“e ЙІaamata, ko fii tippude e kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en hakkille maЙ“Й“e Й—en no eltanii sendindirgol ko boni e ko moЖґЖґi. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Ko Й—un waЙ—i, sutanoЙ—en jannde ЖґoЖґunde nden, feЖґЖґen jannde baggere fii *Almasiihu on nden, hara en fuЙ—Й—itaaki jannugol fii tuubugol kuuЙ—e nawrayЙ—e e mayde Й—en, e fii gomЙ—ingol Alla,  
\v 2 e *lootagol maande kisiyee, e *fawugol juuЙ—e, e immitagol mayЙ“e Й“en, e ЙІaawoore poomayankeere nden.  
\v 3 Ko Й—un waЙ—eten si Allaahu on newnii. 
\p  
\v 4 Fii ndayginananooЙ“e, mettii dokkal kammuyankewal ngal, tawdaa e hendiiЙ“e *Ruuhu SeniiЙ—o on,  
\v 5 mettii moЖґЖґuki daaluyee Alla on wondude e doole aduna aroyoowo on Й“en kan,  
\v 6 si Й“e aru e selude gomЙ—inal ngal, Й“e waawetaake yilteede ka tuubuubuyee han kadi, ko fii haray kamЙ“e tigi Й“e fempitike *ЖЃiЙ—Й—o Alla on, e hoore Й—un Й“e aybinii mo e kene.  
\v 7 Nde leydi yari ndiyan saaЖґoojan soono woo, ndi fuЙ—ini puЙ—i wonduЙ—i e nafa fii mo ndi remanaa on, haray hindi wondi e barki Alla.  
\v 8 Kono si tawii ko bulle e kebbe ndi funnata, haray hinaa ndi huunde, ko ndi Й“adondirndi e kuddi, sakkitora sunneede. 
\p  
\v 9 Hay si men yewtirii nii, yo yiЙ“Й“e amen, haray meЙ—en hoolii hiЙ—on e laawol moЖґЖґol e telen-ma kisiyee on.  
\v 10 Ko fii Alla hinaa mo feewaa, sakko o yejjita kuuЙ—e mon Й—en, e giggol ngol holluЙ—on fii innde makko nden, e golle Й—e waЙ—uЙ—on Й—en e Й—e waЙ—anton Й—en kadi yimЙ“e Alla Й“en.  
\v 11 Kono meЙ—en faalaa yo mo kala e mon hollir nii wakkilaare wootere nden e telen-ma pellital timmungal fii ko tanЖґiniЙ—en kon haa ka sakkitorun.  
\v 12 Ko Й—un waЙ—i, wota on wonu aamuЙ“e, kono ЙІembee Й“en heЙ“irnooЙ“e ndondi fodaandi ndin gomЙ—inal e muЙІal. 
\s1 Fii Fodaari Alla ndi Firtotaako ndin 
\p  
\v 13 Ko Й—un waЙ—i, nde Alla waЙ—annoo Ibraahiima fodaari ndin, o tawno o waawataa woondirde ko Й“uri mo kanko Alla mawnude, o woondiri hoore makko kanko tigi,  
\v 14 o wi'i: 
\q1 В«Pellet, mi waЙ—ay barki e maa fota, 
\q1 mi yaЙІЙІay jurriya maa on yaЙІЙІudee.В»\f r \fr 6:14 \ft 6.14 FuЙ—. 22.17 \f* 
\m  
\v 15 Ko e nder Й—un, Й“ay wonii Ibraahiima habbike e nder muЙІЙІaare, o heЙ“i non ko o fodanoo kon.  
\v 16 E hin-le, yimЙ“e Й“en no woondira ko Й“uri Й“e mawnude, nden woondoore wonana Й“e seedee fii rawnoode kala yeddondiral.  
\v 17 Ko wano non, hakkee ko Alla faalanoo hollude ronooЙ“e fodaari makko ndin Й“en noone no anniyee makko on firtortaa, o waЙ—irno Й—un woondoore  
\v 18 fii, sabu Й—ee kuuЙ—e Й—iЙ—i Й—e waylotaako, Й—e tawata gasataa ka Alla fena, no enen fattiiЙ“e Й“en heЙ“iren wakkilaare tiiЙ—unde fii tamagol e tama'u mo Alla weeЙ“itani en on.  
\v 19 On tama'u no wa'ani en wa saanirgal tiiЙ—ungal holnii fii ngurndan men Й—an, rewoowo ka *wirngallo fii naatugol ka nder *nokkuure hormorde mawnde nden,  
\v 20 Й—un ko ka Almasiihu on naati Й—on fii men wa fertaniiЙ—o en laawol, o woni *yottinoowo mawЙ—o sadaka ka Alla haa poomaa, wano *Maaliki-Siddiiqu non. 
\c 7  
\s1 Fii no Maaliki-Siddiiqu Woniri Yottinoowo Sadaka 
\p  
\v 1 Ko *Maaliki-Siddiiqu on wonnoo lanЙ—o Salaam, e *yottinoowo sadaka ka Alla Jom ЖЃural on. O yahi, o fottoyi e Ibraahiima fewndo ko on iwtata fooloygol lamЙ“e Й“en, kanko Maaliki-Siddiiqu o du'anii mo.  
\v 2 Ibraahiima jonni mo sappaЙ“un e Й—i fow. Ko adii kon taho, innde Maaliki-Siddiiqu nden no firi вЂ№lanЙ—o peewalвЂє. E hoore Й—un kadi ko o lanЙ—o Salaam, e maanaa lanЙ—o Й“uttu.  
\v 3 Kono o alaa neene, o alaa baaba, o alaa iwdi, o alaa fuЙ—Й—oode, o alaa kattudi ngurndan. O wa'i wa *ЖЃiЙ—Й—o Alla, o woni yottinoowo sadaka ka Alla haa poomaa. 
\p  
\v 4 Ndaaree ko haa honto o mawni, on mo Ibraahiima mawЙ—o on tigi jonni sappaЙ“un mun e nder ko o heЙ“oyi kon!  
\v 5 Sariya on toЙ—Й—ii e Й“iЙ“Й“e *Lewi Й“en wonugol yottinooЙ“e sadaka ka Alla e ЖґantooЙ“e sappaЙ“un e hoore ko jamaa *Isra'iila on heЙ“i kon fow, Й—un ko e Й“en ben-gootooЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, fii kala Й“en ko Й“e jurriya Ibraahiima.  
\v 6 Kono Maaliki-Siddiiqu, mo tawdaaka e jurriya Lewi on, o hendike sappaЙ“un Ibraahiima on, e hoore Й—un, o du'anii on hendiiЙ—o fodaariiji Й—in.  
\v 7 E hin-le yeddotaako ko mawЙ—o on du'antoo tosooko on.  
\v 8 E hin-le, e telen-ma yottinooЙ“e sadaka Й“en ka bolondaa Lewi, ko maayayЙ“e woni hendaade sappaЙ“un Й—un, kono e telen-ma Maaliki-Siddiiqu kan, ko wuuruЙ—o woni ko hendii, wano seeditoraa non.  
\v 9 Ka raЙ“Й“inЙ—innde, Lewi, oo wonЙ—o hendaade sappaЙ“un Й—un, o yoЙ“iino ko makko kon rewrude e Ibraahiima.  
\v 10 Ko fii hari himo ka keeci ben makko wa fewndo ko Maaliki-Siddiiqu yahi fottugol e Ibraahiima. 
\s1 Fii no Almasiihu on Woniri wa Maaliki-Siddiiqu 
\p  
\v 11 Ko rewrude e yottinooЙ“e sadaka ka gorol Lewi Й“en jamaa Isra'iila on hendornoo Sariya on. E hin-le, si tawno golle Й“en yottinooЙ“e sadaka ko timmunooЙ—e, harayno ko fii honЙ—un haanannoo waЙ—ugol yottinoowo goo wano Maaliki-Siddiiqu non, hara hinaa wano *Haaruuna non?  
\v 12 Ko fii si aada wonugol yottinooЙ“e sadaka Й“en waylike, haray no haani kadi ka Sariya on waylee.  
\v 13 Ko fii on mo Й—ii piiji wowli fii mun on, ko jeyaaЙ—o e bolondaa goo mo hay gooto toЙ—Й—aaka e mun fii golle *layyorde nden.  
\v 14 E hoore Й—un, wano andirЙ—en non tigi, Joomi men on ko feeЙІuЙ—o e bolondaa *Yahuuda on. E telen-ma wonugol yottinooЙ“e sadaka, Muusaa wowlaali few fii on bolondaa. 
\p  
\v 15 ЖЉunЙ—oo kadi no Й“uri Й“anginde si yottinoowo sadaka goo feeЙІirii wa Maaliki-Siddiiqu,  
\v 16 wontuЙ—o yottinoowo sadaka, hara hinaa tippude e Sariya yuЙ“Й“ondirЙ—o e gorol lannoowol, kono ko tippude e doole ngurndan Й—an lannataa Й—an.  
\v 17 ЖЃay no seeditaa wonde: 
\q1 В«Ko a yottinoowo sadaka ka Alla haa poomaa, 
\q1 wano Maaliki-Siddiiqu non.В»\f s \fr 7:17 \ft 7.17 Zab. 110.4 \f* 
\m  
\v 18 Awa, ko yamiraa Й“aawo Й—oo kon ittaama, sabu lo'ere mun nden e mehiЙ—ugol mun ngol,  
\v 19 ko fii Sariya on waawaali timminde huunde. Kono en addanaama tama'u Й“urЙ—o moЖґЖґude mo Й“adoren Alla. 
\p  
\v 20 ЖЉun non waЙ—aaka e Й“aawo woondoore. ЖЃeya non kaЙІun wontii yottinooЙ“e sadaka ka Alla e Й“aawo woondoore,  
\v 21 kono kanko Iisaa o wontirno Й—un woondoore, Й“ay Alla daalanno mo Й—unЙ—oo: 
\q1 В«Mi woondii, mi firtataa, 
\q1 ko a yottinoowo sadaka ka Alla haa poomaa.В»\f t \fr 7:21 \ft 7.21 Zab. 110.4 \f* 
\m  
\v 22 Ko Й—un waЙ—i si Iisaa wonii holnuЙ—o *ahadi Й“urndi hittude ndin.  
\v 23 E hoore Й—un, hari Й“en yottinooЙ“e sadaka no woodunoo buy, ko fii hari mayde nden no haЙ—i Й“e duumagol e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en.  
\v 24 Kono Iisaa kaЙІun, Й“ay tawii himo wuuri haa poomaa, golle makko yottingol sadaka Й—en lannataa.  
\v 25 Ko Й—un waЙ—i kadi, himo waawi dandude few Й“en wonЙ“e Й“adorde Alla sabu makko kanko Iisaa, Й“ay himo wuuri haa poomaa fii fattanagol Й“e. 
\p  
\v 26 Ko wano on yottinoowo mawЙ—o sadaka tigi haanannoo en, hara ko *seniiЙ—o, mo bonnaali, mo aldaa e junuubu, seeduЙ—o e junuubanke'en, e Й“urЙ—o kammuuli Й—in Й“anteede,  
\v 27 mo hatonjinaa e ittugol sadakaaji wano yottinooЙ“e mawЙ“e Й“en ittirta ЙІande woo sadakaaji fii junuubaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, kamЙ“e tigi taho, e Й—i jamaa on Й—in kadi. Iisaa waЙ—ii Й—un nde wootere ko yoni fii saa'iiji Й—in fow, e nder ko o itti hoore makko sadaka kon.  
\v 28 Sariya on kaЙІun, Й“e toЙ—Й—otoo Й“en fii wonugol yottinooЙ“e sadaka mawЙ“e ko yimЙ“e lo'uЙ“e, kono daalol woondoore nden Й“awto Sariya on toЙ—Й—ike ЖЃiЙ—Й—o on, on wonЙ—o TimminaaЙ—o haa poomaa. 
\c 8  
\s1 Fii Ahadi Heyri ndin e Nokkuure Hormorde Mawnde nden 
\p  
\v 1 Awa e hino nafa toЙ“Й“ere nde wonЙ—en yewtude fii mun nden: hiЙ—en mari wano oo *yottinoowo mawЙ—o sadaka ka Alla, jooЙ—iiЙ—o ka sengo ЙІaamo jullere laamu Alla MawЙ—o on ka kammuuli.  
\v 2 Ko o golloowo ka nder nokkuure hormorde, Й—un ko ka *rewirdu goongaaru, hara hinaa ndu yimЙ“e Й“en darni, kono ko JoomiraaЙ—o on. 
\p  
\v 3 Kala yottinoowo mawЙ—o ko toЙ—Й—oraa ko fii weeЙ“itangol Alla dokke e sadakaaji, bee yottinoowo men mawЙ—o on kadi heЙ“a goЙ—Й—un ko o weeЙ“ita.  
\v 4 Si tawno himo ka hoore leydi, o wonataano yottinoowo sadaka, Й“ay no woodi weeЙ“itooЙ“e dokke, hara ko no yaadiri e Sariya on.  
\v 5 ЖЃen no waЙ—ude dewal ngal tawata ko mbaadi e Й—owdi goongaaji kammuyankeeji Й—in, wano Muusaa Й“anginiranaa non fewndo ko o darnata rewirdu ndun, Alla daalani mo: В«Ndaaru, a waЙ—iray fow noone no holliraЙ—aa non ka hoore fello.В»\f u \fr 8:5 \ft 8.5 Egg. 25.40 \f* 
\v 6 Kono jooni, *Almasiihu on heЙ“ii golle Й“urЙ—e mawnude Й—e Й“eya Й—en, no o woniri non holnuЙ—o *ahadi Й“urndi moЖґЖґude ndin, sincaandi e fodaariiji Й“urЙ—i kelЙ—ude Й—in. 
\p  
\v 7 Si tawno ahadi araniri ndin wonno ndi felnaaki, hewtataano ka wonndi Й—aЙ“Й“ee.  
\v 8 E hin-le ko e hoore feloore Alla daalani jamaa mun on: 
\p В«Kanko JoomiraaЙ—o on o daali: 
\q1 вЂ№Жќalaande no aroya nde mi Жґettodoyta 
\q2 e yimЙ“e *Isra'iila Й“en 
\q2 e yimЙ“e *Yahuuda Й“en ahadi heyri. 
\p  
\v 9 Ndin ahadi wa'oytaa wa 
\q1 ndi mi ahodunoo e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en ndin, 
\q2 wa fewndo mi tambitornoo Й“e juuЙ—e an Й—en 
\q2 fii yaltingol Й“e Misira, 
\q2 ko fii Й“e hunnaali ahadi an ndin.вЂє 
\p В«JoomiraaЙ—o on daali: 
\q1 вЂ№Min kadi jooni mi huccii Й“e. 
\p  
\v 10 E hino non ahadi 
\q1 ndi mi ahodoyta e yimЙ“e Isra'iila Й“en 
\q2 Й“awto Й—ee ЙІalaaЙ—e Й—oo.вЂє 
\p В«JoomiraaЙ—o on daali: 
\q1 вЂ№Mi waЙ—oyay sariyaaji an Й—in ka miijo maЙ“Й“e, 
\q2 mi winda Й—i ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, 
\q1 min mi wona Alla maЙ“Й“e, 
\q2 kamЙ“e kadi Й“e wona jamaa an. 
\p  
\v 11 Hara Й“e hatonjinaa e jannindirgol 
\q1 maa fillitanagol wondiЙ—Й—o mun maa musiЙ—Й—o mun, 
\q2 wi'a: Bee andaa JoomiraaЙ—o on! 
\q1 Ko fii fow andoyay lan, 
\q2 gila e Й“urЙ—o fanЙ—ude on 
\q2 haa e Й“urЙ—o mawnude on. 
\p  
\v 12 Ko fii mi yaafoyto ellaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, 
\q1 mi hakkilanoytaa e junuubaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in.вЂє В»\f w \fr 8:12 \ft 8.8-12 Yer. 31.31-34 \f* 
\m  
\v 13 Ka o inni ndin ahadi heyri Й—on, ko Й—on o watti araniri ndin hinndi. E hin-le hinndi ndin nawyii, no e moggo mulugol. 
\c 9  
\s1 Fii Dewal Adunayankewal ngal e Kammuyankewal ngal 
\p  
\v 1 Ahadi* araniri ndin kadi no marnoo aadaaji mun yaaduЙ—i e dewal, wondude e nokkuure mun hormorde ka aduna Й—oo.  
\v 2 E hoore Й—un, *rewirdu waЙ—anooma. Nokkuure aranere nden e ndun rewirdu no wi'etenoo hormorde, ka joЙ—Й—inirde pitilli nden wonnoo Й—on, e taabal ngal e bireediije weeЙ“itanaaЙ—e JoomiraaЙ—o on Й—en.  
\v 3 E hoore Й—un, Й“aawo *wirngallo Й—immo ngon, tawi no Й—on nokkuure wi'etenoonde *hormorde mawnde nden.  
\v 4 Tawi hinde wondunoo e sunnirde urngallooji tafiraande kaЕ‹Е‹e, e *kankiranwal seeditoore hoobiraangal kaЕ‹Е‹e haa hunditi. Tawi no e nder maggal loonde kaЕ‹Е‹e waЙ—ornde вЂ№*mannaвЂє, wondude e tuggordu *Haaruuna ndun, ndu tawata hari fiinii, e alluuje maande ahadi Й—en.  
\v 5 Tawi no ka hoore kankiranwal nandollaaji *serubiina Mangural ngal, omborde maggal on, Й—un ko ka junuubaaji Й—in yaafetee Й—on, no Й—uwiraa\f y \fr 9:5 \ft 9.5 WoЙ“Й“e kadi no faamira \+it В«Й—uhiraaВ».\+it*\f* gabitanji majji Й—in. Kono hinaa fewndo Й—oo haanuЙ—en wowlugol fensita fii kun kala e koy piihoy. 
\p  
\v 6 Nde tawnoo Й—un fow ko non joЙ—Й—iniranoo, *yottinooЙ“e sadaka ka Alla Й“en naatayno soono woo ka nokkuure aranere e nder rewirdu ndun, fii waЙ—ugol golle diina maЙ“Й“e kan.  
\v 7 Kono ka *nokkuure hormorde mawnde, ko yottinoowo mawЙ—o on tun naataynoo ton nde wootere e nder hitaande nden, e hoore addorgol ЖґiiЖґan ko sakkoo fii hoore mun e fii ellaaji Й—i jamaa on waЙ—iri angal andude.  
\v 8 Ruuhu* SeniiЙ—o on no holliri en telen Й—oo wonde Й—atal nokkuure hormorde mawnde nden udditaaki, fannamaa rewirdu aranuru ndun no lutti.  
\v 9 HiЙ—en mari Й—oo misal feЙІЙІingal goongaaji fewndiiЙ—i hande Й—in. ЖЉun fow no Й“angini wonde dokke e sadakaaji, ko weeЙ“itirantenoo nii Alla, waawataa laЙ“Й“inde Й“ernde on rewiroowo non.  
\v 10 Ko Й—unЙ—oo woni yamirooje neЙ—Й—anke tun yuЙ“Й“ondirЙ—e e ЙІaameteeji e njaramji e noone salligiiji, yamiraaЙ—e haa ЙІande Alla heyЙ—intini piiji Й—in fow. 
\p  
\v 11 Kono *Almasiihu on ardii wa yottinoowo mawЙ—o sadaka fii moЖґЖґereeji fewndiiЙ—i Й—in. O taЖґiti rewirdu Й“urndu mawnude ndun e Й“urndu timmude ndun, ndu tawata hinaa darniraandu juuЙ—e yimЙ“e, e maanaa ndun hinaa ndu oo aduna.  
\v 12 O naatii ka nokkuure hormorde mawnde nde wootere ko yoni haa poomaa, rewrude e ЖґiiЖґan makko Й—an tigi, hara hinaa rewrude e ЖґiiЖґan ciikuliiji e ЙІalbi. Ko nii o yeЙ—iri en cottudi poomayankeeri.  
\v 13 Si tawii ЖґiiЖґan ciikuliiji e ga'i na'i e ndoondi wiige, ko wiccitee junjee e hoore yimЙ“e Й“e laaЙ“aa, no laЙ“Й“ina Й“e ka Й“andu,  
\v 14 kono Almasiihu on kaЙІun ko hoore mun tigi ittani Alla sadaka e Й“aawo ella, e hoore ardoreede Ruuhu Poomayankeejo on, ko haa honto non ЖґiiЖґan makko Й—an laЙ“Й“inta Й“erЙ—e men, itta en e kuuЙ—e nawrayЙ—e en e mayde, fii no rewiren Alla WuuruЙ—o on! 
\p  
\v 15 Ko Й—un waЙ—i si ko kanko woni holnuЙ—o ahadi heyri ndin, fii yo noddaaЙ“e Й“en hendo ndondi poomayankeeri ndi Alla fodi Й“e ndin. Ko fii mayde makko nden wonii sadaka fii sottugol Й“e e Й—in bonnereeji waЙ—aaЙ—i ka fewndo ahadi hinndi.  
\v 16 Ko fii, ka wasiyannde nden woni Й—on, haray no haani ka mayde wasiyiiЙ—o on andee.  
\v 17 Wasiyannde nden non laatike woo Й“awto mayde nden, ko fii nde alaa nafa fewndo wasiyiiЙ—o on wuuri.  
\v 18 Ko Й—un waЙ—i, ahadi araniri ndin tigi, ndi udditaaka e Й“aawo hibbugol ЖґiiЖґan.  
\v 19 ЖЃay Muusaa gaynii weeЙ“itande jamaa on fow kala yamiroore, wano Й—e woniri non ka Sariya, o Жґetti ЖґiiЖґan ga'i na'i e ciikuliiji e ndiyan e gaara boЙ—e, o wicciri deftere nden e jamaa on baapal no wi'ee *hisoopu,  
\v 20 e hoore himo wi'a: В«ЖЉunЙ—oo ko ЖґiiЖґan ahadi ndi Alla yamiri fii mon ndin nii.В»\f Жґ \fr 9:20 \ft 9.20 Egg. 24.8 \f* 
\v 21 Ko wano non kadi, o wicciri rewirdu ndun e aalaaji gollirteeЙ—i fii diina Й—in ЖґiiЖґan.  
\v 22 E telen-ma Sariya on, fayda fow ko ЖґiiЖґan laЙ“Й“iniraa, ko fii yaafuyee alaa e Й“aawo hibbugol ЖґiiЖґan. 
\p  
\v 23 ЖЉin aalaaji lontiiЙ—i goongaaji kammuyankeeji, no haanunoo laЙ“Й“inireede oo noone Й—oo, kono no haaniri non ka haqiiqaaji kammuyankeeji Й—in laЙ“Й“iniree sadakaaji Й“urЙ—i moЖґЖґude.  
\v 24 Ko fii Almasiihu on naataali e nder nokkuure hormorde waЙ—iraande juuЙ—e neЙ—Й—anke, ЙІembinaande goongaare nden, kono ko ka kammu tigi fii no o weeЙ“itorana en jooni yeeso Alla.  
\v 25 O naatiraali fii ittugol hoore makko sadaka soono woo, wano yottinooЙ“e mawЙ“e Й“en naatirta hitaande woo ka nokkuure hormorde mawnde wondude e ЖґiiЖґan Й—an tawata wonaa ЖґiiЖґan makko.  
\v 26 Ko fii, si hinaano Й—un, Almasiihu on tampayno soono woo gila ka fuЙ—Й—oode aduna on. Kono jooni, ka lannoode jamaanuuji, o feeЙІii nde wootere ko yoni fii saa'iiji Й—in fow fii bonnitugol junuubaaji e nder ko o itti hoore makko sadaka kon.  
\v 27 Nde tawnoo no maranaa yimЙ“e Й“en maayugol nde wootere pet, Й“awto Й—un ЙІaawoore nden waЙ—a,  
\v 28 ko wano non Almasiihu on ittiri hoore mun sadaka nde wootere pet fii ronditagol junuubaaji yimЙ“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e. Awa, o artoyay kadi, hara hinaa fii ronditagol junuubaaji, kono ko fii dandugol Й“en habbornooЙ“e mo kisiyee. 
\c 10  
\s1 Fii Sadaka mo Almasiihu on Itti on 
\p  
\v 1 E hoore Й—un, wonaa Sariya on tigi woni haqiiqaaji aroyaynooЙ—i Й—in, kono ko mbaadi mun tun. O waawataa few laatinde Й“en Й“adorayЙ“e non Alla timmuЙ“e, rewrude e on sadaka gooto jokkondirЙ—o hitaande woo hitaande.  
\v 2 Si o waawayno, harayno neeЙ“ii ko Й“en waЙ—aynooЙ“e Й—in sadakaaji acci, harayno Й“e laЙ“Й“inaama nde wootere ko yoni haa poomaa, harayno kadi Й“ernde maЙ“Й“e felataa Й“e e telen-ma junuubu woo.  
\v 3 Kono, Й—in sadakaaji andintinay en hitaande kala fii junuubaaji Й—in.  
\v 4 Ko fii waawataa ka ЖґiiЖґan ga'i na'i e ciikuliiji monta junuubaaji. 
\p  
\v 5 Ko Й—un waЙ—i, e nder naatugol e nder aduna on, *Almasiihu on no wi'i: 
\q1 В«Wonaa sadakaaji maa dokke faalaЙ—aa, 
\q1 kono a waЙ—anii lan Й“andu. 
\p  
\v 6 A weltoraali sadaka sunneteeЙ—o, 
\q1 maa ko sakkaa fii junuubu. 
\p  
\v 7 Awa mi wi'i: вЂ№E hino lan, mi arii 
\q1 fii waЙ—ugol faale maa on, yaa an Alla, 
\q1 wano fii an windori non e nder ndee deftere taggiinde.вЂє В»\f z \fr 10:7 \ft 10.7 Zab. 40.7-9 \f* 
\m  
\v 8 Himo wi'i taho: В«A yiЙ—aali e a weltoraali sadakaaji e dokke e sadakaaji sunneteeЙ—i e sadakaaji fii junuubaaji, waЙ—iranooЙ—i no yaadiri e Sariya on.В» 
\p  
\v 9 E hoore Й—un o wi'i kadi: В«E hino lan, mi arii fii waЙ—ugol faale maa on.В» O ittii aranun Й—un fii sincugol Й—immun Й—un.  
\v 10 Awa, ko sabu faale Alla on *laЙ“Й“inaЙ—en fii wonugol yimЙ“e makko, rewrude e oo sadaka mo Iisaa Almasiihu on ittiri Й“andu mun ndun tigi nde wootere ko yoni haa poomaa. 
\p  
\v 11 Kala *yottinoowo sadaka ka Alla no ka gollata Й—on ЙІande woo fii waЙ—ugol golle mun diina Й—en, e ittugol sadakaaji gooti ЙІande woo, Й—i tawata waawataa ittude junuubaaji few.  
\v 12 Almasiihu on non kaЙІun, o waЙ—ii sadaka gooto bajjo fii junuubaaji Й—in, yonuЙ—o haa poomaa, awa kadi himo jooЙ—ii ka sengo ЙІaamo Alla,  
\v 13 himo sabbii Й—on haa Alla waЙ—a ayЙ“e makko Й“en ka ley koyЙ—e makko.  
\v 14 Ko dokkal bajjal o timminiri haa poomaa wonaaЙ“e *laЙ“Й“ineede fii wonugol yimЙ“e Alla Й“en.  
\v 15 Ko Й—un *Ruuhu SeniiЙ—o on seeditanii en kadi. Ko fii himo wi'i taho: 
\p  
\v 16 В«JoomiraaЙ—o on daali: 
\q1 вЂ№E hino *ahadi ndi mi Жґettodoyta e maЙ“Й“e ndin: 
\q1 ЖЃawto Й—ee ЙІalaaЙ—e Й—oo, 
\q1 mi waЙ—oyay sariyaaji an Й—in ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, 
\q1 mi windoya Й—i ka hakkille maЙ“Й“e.вЂє В» 
\m  
\v 17 O Й“eyditi e Й—un: 
\q1 В«Mi anditoytaa hande kadi fii junuubaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in 
\q1 e angal peewal maЙ“Й“e ngal.В»\f a \fr 10:17 \ft 10.17 Yer. 31.33-34 \f* 
\m  
\v 18 Ko fii ka junuubaaji Й—in yaafaa Й—on, haray alaa ko sakkee fii junuubu. 
\s1 Fii GomЙ—inal YimЙ“e Й“en 
\p  
\v 19 Ko Й—un waЙ—i, yo musiЙ“Й“e an, Й“ay hiЙ—en mari hoolaare fii naatugol ka *nokkuure hormorde mawnde sabu oo sadaka ЖґiiЖґan Iisaa  
\v 20 Й—an o udditirani en laawol kesol wurngol, rewrungol ka *wirngallo, ngon-le ko Й“andu makko ndun,  
\v 21 e Й“ay kadi hiЙ—en mari yottinoowo mawЙ—o wonЙ—o ka suudu Alla,  
\v 22 Й“adoren Alla Й“ernde nunЙ—unde e gomЙ—inal heewungal pellital, e Й“ernde laЙ“Й“inaande kala miijooji bonЙ—i, e Й“andu lootiraandu ndiyan laaЙ“uЙ—an.  
\v 23 Wonen catiiЙ“e tabiti e tama'u mo qirritiЙ—en on, ko fii WaЙ—anЙ—o en Й—in fodaariiji on ko Sella-findeejo.  
\v 24 Miijondiranen ko honno waaweten wakkilindirde ka giggol e ka kuuЙ—e moЖґЖґe.  
\v 25 Wota en terto mottondiral men ngal, wano woЙ“Й“e woowiri non. Kono wakkilindiren fodde hiЙ—en yi'ude ЙІalaande nden no Й“adaade. 
\p  
\v 26 Ko fii si en duumike waЙ—ugol junuubu e nder tewaare Й“awto en hendaade gandal goonga on, haray sadaka alaa hande kadi fii junuubaaji,  
\v 27 kono ko habbannde ЙІaawoore hulЙ“iniinde e nguleendi yiite hebuliinge sunnugol murtuЙ“e Й“en.  
\v 28 Si goЙ—Й—o bonniino Sariya Muusaa on, o wareteno, o yaafetaake, e hoore seeditoore Й—iЙ—o maa tato.  
\v 29 E miijo mon onon, si goЙ—Й—o hayfinii *ЖЃiЙ—Й—o Alla on, si o jogitorii ЖґiiЖґan ahadi Й—an wa Й—an aldaa e fiira, Й—an Й—an o *laЙ“Й“iniraa, e si o hoynii Ruuhu Allaahu on, on Jom Sulfu, e hara on miijaaki himo handi e lette Й“urЙ—e muusude kadi?  
\v 30 Ko fii hiЙ—en andi on Wi'uЙ—o: В«Ko min yottagol woodani, ko min yoЙ“oytaВ», e hoore Й—un: В«JoomiraaЙ—o on ЙІaaway jamaa mun on.В»\f b \fr 10:30 \ft 10.30 YaЙІ. 32.35-36 \f* 
\v 31 No hulЙ“inii yanugol e juuЙ—e Alla WuuruЙ—o on! 
\p  
\v 32 Anditee liddu Й—un ka saa'iiji arani, Й“awto Alla ndayginande on, on Е‹aЙІЙІino satteende tiiЙ—unde e nder tippiro muusungo.  
\v 33 Ko fii e saa'i goo on hoynano, cukkaЙ—on e kene, e saa'i goo jonnindirЙ—on juuЙ—e e Й“en waЙ—iranooЙ“e wano non.  
\v 34 E hoore Й—un, yurmaЙ—on sokaaЙ“e Й“en, jaЙ“uЙ—on kadi e nder weltaare yo on jatte keyeeji mon Й—in, sabu andugol mon hiЙ—on mari keyee Й“urЙ—o moЖґЖґude, luttoowo.  
\v 35 Awa wota on accitu hoolaare mon addaynde mbarjaari mawndi nden.  
\v 36 Ko fii hiЙ—on haani Е‹aЙІЙІaade, fii, nde timminoyЙ—on faale Alla on, yo on hendoyo ko o fodi on kon. 
\p  
\v 37 Ko fii e nder saa'ihun nii: 
\q1 В«HaanuЙ—o arude on aray, neeЙ“ataa. 
\p  
\v 38 FeewuЙ—o an on non wuuriray gomЙ—inal. 
\q1 Kono si o yiltitike, 
\q1 wonkii an kin weltanoytaako mo.В»\f c \fr 10:38 \ft 10.38 Hab. 2.3-4 \f* 
\m  
\v 39 Enen-le hinaa en yiltorooЙ“e Й“aawo fii hayrugol, kono ko en gomЙ—inЙ“e fii dandegol. 
\c 11  
\s1 Fii SeeditorЙ“e GomЙ—inal ka Ahadi Hinndi 
\p  
\v 1 E hin-le, gomЙ—inal ngal ko pellital fii piiji Й—i tanЖґiniЙ—en, e hoolaare fii piiji Й—i en yi'aali taho.  
\v 2 Alla kulji mawЙ“e Й“aawo Й—oo Й“en sabu gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal. 
\p  
\v 3 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal wonЙ—en andirde aduna on ko daaluyee Alla on tagiraa. Ko Й—un waЙ—i ko yi'eten kon iwraa e ko yi'otoo. 
\p  
\v 4 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal Haabiila yeЙ—iri Alla sadaka Й“urЙ—o moЖґЖґude mo Qaayiina on. O kuljiraa feewuЙ—o sabu ngal gomЙ—inal. Alla tigi kulji Й—en dokke makko. Fii kala kanko Haabiila o maayii, kono ngal gomЙ—inal no Й“anginde fii makko. 
\p  
\v 5 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal kadi Hanuuka Жґentiniraa fii wota o andu mayde nden. En yi'ataa mo hande kadi sabu Allaahu on Жґentinno mo. Ko fii, ado o Жґentineede, hari o heЙ“iino kuluujaa wonde himo weltini Alla.  
\v 6 Awa, e Й“aawo gomЙ—inal, gasataa ka ontigi weltina Alla, ko fii on Й“adotooЙ—o mo no haani gomЙ—inde wonde kanko Alla himo woodaa, gomЙ—ina kadi ko kanko woni yoЙ“oowo Й—aЙ“Й“ooЙ“e mo Й“en. 
\p  
\v 7 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal fahin Nuuhu moЖґЖґinirnoo laana fii dandugol Й“eynguure mun nden. Ko nii o teddiniri ko Alla *hiitaninoo mo fii ko aroyta yi'aaka taho kon. ЖЃay o warrii non kanko Nuuhu, tawi o hollii wonde yimЙ“e aduna on ko felniiЙ“e. Alla jogori Nuuhu feewuЙ—o sabu gomЙ—inal makko ngal. 
\p  
\v 8 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal kadi Ibraahiima Й—oftori noddaandu ndu Alla noddi mo ndun fii yahugol e leydi ndi o ronoyta ndin. O yahi e hoore o andaa ka o woni yahude.  
\v 9 Ko gomЙ—inal o hoЙ—iri e ndin leydi fodaandi wa leydi jananiri, o hoЙ—i e nder cuuЙ—i bagi. Issaaqa* e Yaaquuba kadi hoЙ—iri non, Й“e ronidi e makko fodaari wootiri ndin.  
\v 10 Ko fii hari, kanko Ibraahiima himo habbii hoЙ—o ngo tawata didol cuuЙ—i mun no tiiЙ—i, ngo tawata ko Alla eЙ“Й“i, darni.  
\v 11 Ko sabu gomЙ—inal ngal kadi, fii kala Saarata kaЙІun ko mo jiidotaako, o heЙ“iri feere jurriyagol e nder nayeewu makko, Й“ay himo hoolii wonde Alla ko hunnoowo ko o fodi kon.  
\v 12 Ko Й—un waЙ—i si neЙ—Й—o gooto, mo tawata mayde mun nden heЙ“iino Й—un, heЙ“i jurriya Й“urЙ—o koode Й—en ka kammu Й—uuЙ—ude e njaareendi ndin ka sera baharu, ko tawata en waawataa limude. 
\p  
\v 13 Ko e nder gomЙ—inal ngal Й“e fow Й“e maayi e Й“aawo hendagol piiji fodaaЙ—i Й—in, kono Й“e haynino Й—i ka woЙ—Й—i, Й“e weltori, e nder qirritagol ko Й“e tuЕ‹arankeeЙ“e e jananЙ“e ka leydi.  
\v 14 YewtirayЙ“e nii Й“en hollii no laaЙ“iri wonde hiЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ande hoore maЙ“Й“e leydi heyri.  
\v 15 Si tawno non Й“e wulЙ—ano ka Й“e iwi ton, Й“e heЙ“ayno feere no Й“e yiltora.  
\v 16 Kono ka haqiiqa hiЙ“e himmannoo nokkuure Й“urnde moЖґЖґude, Й—un ko ka kammu. Ko Й—un waЙ—i Alla hersiraa noddeede Alla maЙ“Й“e, ko fii o moЖґЖґinanii Й“e hoЙ—o. 
\p  
\v 17 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal kadi Ibraahiima weeЙ“itiri Issaaqa fii layyagol fewndo ko Allaahu on ndarndii mo. Hari himo e fii sakkagol Issaaqa, Й“iЙ—Й—o makko bajjo on, kanko hendinooЙ—o fodaariiji Й—in,  
\v 18 Й—un ko on mo Allaahu on daalannoo wonde: В«Ko e Issaaqa jurriya maa on nodditirtee.В»  
\v 19 Himo joginoo wonde Alla ko WaawuЙ—o hay immintingol mayЙ—o e hakkunde mayЙ“e Й“en, ko Й—un waЙ—i si o hettitiri Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on wa immitiiЙ—o e mayde. 
\p  
\v 20 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal kadi Issaaqa du'orani Yaaquuba e *Iisu fii ko aroyta kon. 
\p  
\v 21 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal fahin, fewndo Yaaquuba maayata, o du'orani mo kala e Й“iЙ“Й“e Yuusufu Й“en, o ugginii e hoore tuggordu makko ndun, o sujjani Alla. 
\p  
\v 22 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal fahin, Й“ay Й“adike ka Yuusufu maaya, o maandiniri fii eggudu *Banii-Isra'iila'en ndun *Misira, o waЙ—i kadi yamirooje fii Жґi'e makko Й—en. 
\p  
\v 23 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal kadi, Й“ay Muusaa jibinaama, mawЙ“e makko Й“en suuЙ—iri mo lebbi tati, Й“ay Й“e tawii boobo on no labaa fota, awa kadi Й“e hulaano yamiroore lanЙ—o on. 
\p  
\v 24 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal kadi, Й“ay Muusaa mawnii, o salori wi'eede ko o geЙ—al jiwo Fir'awna on.  
\v 25 O tawi ko tampindineede e jamaa Alla on Й“urani mo, edii weltorgol junuubu e nder saa'ihun.  
\v 26 Tawi himo miijii wonde ko aybinireede wa *Almasiihu on Й“uri jogaade ngalu tiiЙ—ungu edii ngu Misira ngun, ko fii himo ndaaraynoo ka muutii telen ka njoddi.  
\v 27 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal o yaltiri Misira e Й“aawo Й—enЖґagol tikkere lanЙ—o on, Й“ay himo catornoo wa sutiiЙ—o on mo yi'otaako.  
\v 28 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal kadi o waЙ—iri *Juldeere Yawtaneede nden, e wujugol ЖґiiЖґan fii wota muloowo dikkuruuЙ“e on meemu ko dikkoranaa Isra'iilayankeeЙ“e Й“en kon. 
\p  
\v 29 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal fahin Й“e taЖґitiri *Baharu BoЙ—eejo on wa leydi yorndi, kono nde MisirayankooЙ“e Й“en eЙ“Й“unoo waЙ—irgol non, Й“e yoolino. 
\p  
\v 30 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal kadi tata on Yeerikoo yaniri, Й“ay Й“e gaynii taaraade mo e nder balЙ—e jeeЙ—iЙ—i.  
\v 31 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal kadi waЙ—i si *Raabi, oo debbo cagaajo, maydaano e heeferЙ“e Й“en, sabu ko o wernirnoo tefooЙ“e Й“en kon Й“uttu. 
\p  
\v 32 Ko honЙ—un mi wi'ata kadi? Saa'i on yonantaa lan si tawii mi wowlay mi fensita fii oo wi'eteeЙ—o *Gadawna e *Baaraka e Samsuuna e Yiftaaha e Daawuuda e Samu'iila e annabaaЙ“e Й“en.  
\v 33 Ko gomЙ—inal ngal Й“e fooliri laamateeriiji, Й“e tabintini peewal, Й“e heЙ“i fodaariiji, Й“e ombi sekko ngayuuje.  
\v 34 ЖЃe Й—annini giiteeli bonnooji, Й“e daЙ—i mbelndi kaafa, Й“e heewi doole fii kala hiЙ“e lo'unoo, Й“e hollitii ka nder hareeji, Й“e raЙ—ii koneeli jananЙ“e Й“en.  
\v 35 RewЙ“e yi'i mayЙ“e mun no immitoo. WoЙ“Й“e goo kadi lettaa, Й“e salii sotteede fii no Й“e heЙ“ira ummutal Й“urngal moЖґЖґude.  
\v 36 WoЙ“Й“e Й“en heЙ“i aybineede e focceede, e hoore jolkeede sokee.  
\v 37 WoЙ“Й“e Й“en wariraa kaaЖґe, woЙ“Й“e Й“en tampinaa taЖґaa Й—iЙ—i, maa wariraa kaafa. WoЙ“Й“e nawri ngurndan mun Й—an yaarugol hen fow, hara no Й“ornii guri baali maa be'i, Й“illorЙ“e Й—i fow, cukkee tampinee.  
\v 38 Hari aduna on handaa e Й“en, Й“e tawata wonundeeji mun ko ka wulaaji e ka pelle e ka pammeeje e ka gayЙ—e. 
\p  
\v 39 ЖЃen kuljiranooЙ“e sabu gomЙ—inal mun ngal fow non, hendaaki ko Й“e fodanoo kon.  
\v 40 Ko fii Alla no eЙ“Й“ani en goЙ—Й—un ko Й“uri moЖґЖґude, fii wota Й“e laato timmuЙ“e e Й“aawo men. 
\c 12  
\s1 Fii no Alla Wurtirta en wa ЖЃiЙ“Й“e mun 
\p  
\v 1 ЖЃay wano ngal dental mawngal seedeeЙ“e no hundi en, bugitoЙ—en kala dongal e junuubu ko falli en no weeЙ“iri, dogiren wakkilaare dogudu ndu eЙ“Й“anaЙ—en ndun.  
\v 2 PunnoЙ—en Iisaa, on wonЙ—o daЖґЖґere gomЙ—inal ngal, on timminoowo ngal. ЖЃay himo sutinoo weltaare maraniinde mo nden, o jaЙ“uno *leggal altindiraangal ngal, o yawitii hersa, o jooЙ—ii ka sengo ЙІaamo jullere laamu Alla.  
\v 3 Miijitee fii on Е‹aЙІЙІiiЙ—o ndee liddannde nde junuubanke'en liddii mo, fii wota ronkere heЙ“u on haa Й“erЙ—e mon maaya. 
\p  
\v 4 E hin-le e nder gertagol mon junuubu ngol, on dartaaki haa ЖґiiЖґan mon Й—an hibbi.  
\v 5 Awa kadi on yejjitii kongol ngol Allaahu on wakkiliri on ngol wa Й“iЙ“Й“e makko: 
\q1 В«ЖЃiЙ—Й—o an, wota a jogitor wurtannde JoomiraaЙ—o on no hayfiri, 
\q1 awa kadi wota Й“ernde maa maayu nde o wurtu-maa. 
\q1  
\v 6 Ko fii ko mo JoomiraaЙ—o on yiЙ—i, o wurtata, 
\q1 o yaggina kala mo o jaЙ“i yo wonu Й“iЙ—Й—o makko.В»\f d \fr 12:6 \ft 12.6 Tin. 3.11-12 \f* 
\m  
\v 7 Wakkilee tampereeji mon Й—in, ko Й—in woni on wurtude. Ko wa Й“iЙ“Й“e Alla woni on jogitorde. Ko hombo woni Й“iЙ—Й—o mo ben mun wurtataa?  
\v 8 Kono si on woorike wurtannde nde fow heЙ“ata nden, haray ko on fattuuЙ“e, hinaa on Й“iЙ“Й“e.  
\v 9 ЖЃay en heЙ“ii baabaaЙ“e ka aduna Й—oo wurtaynooЙ“e en, Й“e teddinnoЙ—en, ko haa honto non haanuЙ—en yankinanaade Ben ruuhuuji men Й—in fii no wuuriren!  
\v 10 Ko fii baabiraaЙ“e men Й“en no wurtaynoo en e nder saa'ihun nii, Й“ay Й“e tawno ko ko moЖґЖґi, kono Alla ko woni en wurtirde ko fii nafa men on tigi, fii no tawreЙ—en e laaЙ“al makko ngal.  
\v 11 No fellitaa fewndo wurteede nandaa e huunde weltinnde, kono ko satteende. Kono Й“awto Й—un, battane ngurndan feewuЙ—an wonЙ—an e nder Й“uttu no maranii Й“en wurtaaЙ“e. 
\p  
\v 12 Ko Й—un waЙ—i si mi wi'ay on, Й“antee juuЙ—e mon lo'uЙ—e Й—en, sattinon koppi mon lo'uЙ—i Й—in,  
\v 13 yo koyЙ—e mon Й—en jokku laawi feewuЙ—i Й—in, fii wota laЖґooje Й—en worgito, kono Й—e sella. 
\s1 Fii no Hittiniren e Noddaandu Heyru ndun 
\p  
\v 14 Etee no wondiron e fow e nder Й“uttu, wuuron e nder laaЙ“al, ko fii Й“aawo maggal hay gooto yi'ataa JoomiraaЙ—o on.  
\v 15 Reenee fii wota hay gooto Е‹akkire moЖґЖґere Alla nden, wota Й—aЙ—ol haaЙ—ungol woo kadi funtu, wona sabu jiiЙ“oldu haa raaЙ“a buy e mon.  
\v 16 Reenee fii wota hay gooto e mon jeenu, maa wona keefeero wa *Iisu, on yeeyitunooЙ—o afoyaagal mun ngal fii nafakka gooto.  
\v 17 HiЙ—on andi, Й“awto Й—un, wa fewndo ko o faalaa heЙ“ude du'aa ben makko on, o bugitano, ko fii o heЙ“aano feere waylugol miijo ben makko ngon, fii kala hari himo Й—aЙ“Й“irde Й—un gonЙ—i. 
\p  
\v 18 Ko fii onon, on Й“adaaki fello ngo waaweten meemude, e yiite huЙ“Й“unge e Й—owdi duule e niЙ“e e nduluuru,  
\v 19 maa hito *liital, maa hawa ka *Isra'iilayankeeЙ“e Й“en nanunoo kan haa Й“e wi'i wota Й“e Й“eyditane hay kongol,  
\v 20 ko fii Й“e townataano sifa ndee yamiroore tiiЙ—unde Й—oo: В«Hay si mummunte meemiino ngon fello, warirteno kaaЖґe.В»\f Й— \fr 12:20 \ft 12.20 Egg. 19.12-13 \f* 
\v 21 Hakkee ko Й—un hulЙ“ininoo, Muusaa wi'i: В«Mi diwnii hakkee ko mi huli!В»\f e \fr 12:21 \ft 12.21 YaЙІ. 9.19 \f* 
\p  
\v 22 Kono onon, on Й“adike Fello *Siyuuna ngon e saare Alla WuuruЙ—o on, Й—un ko *Yerusalaam kammuyankeejo on, e guluuje malaa'ika mottondiri e nder weltaare.  
\v 23 On Й“adike dental dikkuruuЙ“e Alla Й“en, Й“en Й“e tawata no windii ka kammuuli. On Й“adike Alla, on Жќaawoowo yimЙ“e Й“en fow, e ruuhuuji feewuЙ“e timminaaЙ“e Й“en.  
\v 24 On Й“adike Iisaa, on holnuЙ—o *ahadi heyri ndin, e ЖґiiЖґan makko hibbaaЙ—an, Й—an seeЙ—itoore mun Й“uri moЖґЖґude Й—an Haabiila Й—an. 
\p  
\v 25 Awa reenee wota on salo heЙ—aade on WonЙ—o on yewtude. ЖЃen Isra'iilayankeeЙ“e, salinooЙ“e heЙ—aade on WonnooЙ—o Й“e yamirde ka hoore leydi, Й“e daЙ—aano lette Й—en. E ko honno non woniranta en si en huccii on WonЙ—o en yewtude ka kammuuli dow?  
\v 26 On mo hito mun dimbi leydi ndin, waЙ—ii jooni ndii fodaari Й—oo: В«Awa mi dimbitoyay nde wootere kadi, hinaa non leydi ndin tun, kono hay kammu ngun.В»\f f \fr 12:26 \ft 12.26 Haj. 2.6 \f* 
\v 27 Ngol daalol В«nde wootere kadiВ» no laaЙ“i poy holli wonde kala ko tagaa dimboto, dilla, fii no goongaaji Й—i gasataa dimbaade Й—in luttira.  
\v 28 ЖЃay laamu ngu hendotoЙ—en ngun hinaa dimbotoongu, weltanoЙ—en Alla, kurkanoЙ—en mo noone no welirta mo e nder teddungal e kulol.  
\v 29 Ko fii Alla men on ko yiite sunnoowe. 
\c 13  
\s1 Fii Salminaango e Wakkilingol 
\p  
\v 1 Yo giggol siЙ—Й—ankaaku ngol duumo.  
\v 2 Wota on yejjitu wernugol. Ko fii e nder warrugol non woЙ“Й“e wernii malaa'ikaaЙ“e, hara Й“e andaa.  
\v 3 Anditee fii kasooЙ“e Й“en, wa si tawii hiЙ—on sokidaa e maЙ“Й“e, e wonaaЙ“e e tampineede Й“en, wa si tawii ko onon wonaa tampineede. 
\p  
\v 4 Yo mo kala teddin dewgal ngal, awa kadi yo ЖґettindirЙ“e Й“en yonindiran, ko fii telen-ma Й—on, Alla ЙІaaway fijooЙ“e Й“en e jinooЙ“e Й“en.  
\v 5 Wota on ardinir ngurndan mon Й—an giggol kaalisi, yondinoree ko jogiЙ—on kon fewndo Й—oo. Ko fii Alla tigi no wi'i: В«Mi accitataa ma e mi tertotaako ma few.В»\f g \fr 13:5 \ft 13.5 YaЙІ. 31.6 \f* 
\p  
\v 6 Mo kala e men no waawi wi'ude e nder pellital: 
\q1 В«Ko JoomiraaЙ—o on woni faabo an ngon, mi hulataa. 
\q1 Ko honЙ—un neЙ—Й—o waawanimmi?В»\f h \fr 13:6 \ft 13.6 Zab. 118.6-7 \f* 
\m  
\v 7 Anditee fii ardotooЙ“e on Й“en, Й“en feЙІЙІinannooЙ“e on daaluyee Alla on, miijitoЙ—on fii battane no Й“e wuuriri non, ЙІembon gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal.  
\v 8 Awa Iisaa Almasiihu on ko gooto, o waylotaako hanki e hande e haa poomaa. 
\p  
\v 9 Wota on jaЙ“u kala noone janndeeji janani selna on. Ko fii no moЖґЖґi ka Й“ernde nden tiiЙ—iniree moЖґЖґere Alla nden, hara hinaa sariyaaji fii ЙІaameteeji Й—i nafaali huunde Й“en jokkuЙ“e Й—i.  
\v 10 Ko fii hiЙ—en mari *layyorde nde tawata haananaa gollooЙ“e ka *rewirdu adunayankeeru ЙІaamugol ko sakkaa Й—on kon.  
\v 11 Ko fii *yottinooЙ“e mawЙ“e sadaka Й“en sakkorayno ЖґiiЖґan ka nokkuure hormorde, kono tebbeeli Й—in sunneteno ka Й“aawo hoЙ—o.  
\v 12 Ko Й—un waЙ—i si Iisaa kadi tampuno ka Й“aawo hoЙ—o fii *laЙ“Й“inirgol jamaa on ЖґiiЖґan makko Й—an tigi.  
\v 13 Awa enen kadi, yalten ka Й“aawo hoЙ—o fii yahugol e makko, e hoore rondagol hersa ka o rondinoo kan.  
\v 14 Ko fii en maraa Й—oo hoЙ—o tabitungo, kono hiЙ—en Й—aЙ“Й“ude aroyayngo ngon.  
\v 15 E innde makko kanko Iisaa, duumoЙ—en e waЙ—angol Alla sadaka mantoore, e maanaa sadaka yaltoowo e toni jantotooЙ—i innde makko nden.  
\v 16 Awa wota on weddito e waЙ—ugol moЖґЖґere e wallindirgol, ko Й—ii woni sadakaaji Й—i Alla jaЙ“ata weltora. 
\p  
\v 17 ЖЉoftee ardotooЙ“e on Й“en, yankinanoЙ—on Й“e. Ko fii hiЙ“e ayni fota wonkiiji mon Й—in, wa hunitoytooЙ“e ka Alla. Awa etee Й“e waЙ—a Й—un e hoore weltaare, hara hinaa no mettirta Й“e. Si hinaa Й—un, nafoytaa on. 
\p  
\v 18 Awa toranee men: meЙ—en felliti wonde meЙ—en mari Й“ernde laaЙ“unde e nder faalegol nawrude ngurndan amen Й—an no feewiri e kala huunde.  
\v 19 Mi torike on fow tentinii toragol fii yo Allaahu on newnanan yiltitagol ka mon no yaawiri. 
\p  
\v 20 Yo Alla Jom ЖЃuttu on, on ArtirЙ—o e hakkunde mayЙ“e Й“en Iisaa Joomi men, Ngaynaako MawЙ—o baali Й—in, rewrude e ЖґiiЖґan *ahadi poomayankeeri ndin,  
\v 21 yo o wawnu on e kala ko moЖґЖґi fii waЙ—ugol faale makko on, o waЙ—a e men ko welata mo, tippude e Iisaa Almasiihu on, on mo mangural wonani haa poomaa. Aamiina! 
\p  
\v 22 Mi torike on, yo musiЙ“Й“e an, jaЙ“ugol ngol kongol wakkilinayngol, ko fii mi windanii on, mi raЙ“Й“inЙ—inii. 
\p  
\v 23 Awa andee wonde, Timotee, oo musiЙ—Й—o men, yaltinaama ka kaso. Si o hewtitii law, mi yaaday e makko, men yiida e mon.  
\v 24 Hiwranee lan ardotooЙ“e on Й“en fow e yimЙ“e Alla Й“en fow. ЖЃee Й“e Italii salminii on. 
\p  
\v 25 Yo moЖґЖґere JoomiraaЙ—o on wonu e hoore mon on fow.